 I go to a convenience store to buy a weapon, but they don't sell them. Convenience stores are stupid. They should take a little space where they have a lot of stationery and put some insecticides. Insecticides don't hurt, and when people come to buy them, it's an emergency, so they'll buy them even if the price is a little high.
 
